videos.description: Shea Patterson dumps it off to Nico Collins who finds a lane and takes it to the house for an early Michigan TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Collins skirts the sidelines for a 48-yard Michigan TD) 2019/09/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Collins skirts the sidelines for a 48-yard Michigan TD

videos.description: Shea Patterson calls his own number off the play action and finds a wide open lane for a short touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Patterson calls his own number 2-yard TD) 2019/09/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Patterson calls his own number 2-yard TD

videos.description: Shea Patterson is no stranger to the end zone today as he dives in for his second touchdown.
videos.headline: Patterson dives in for second TD of half

videos.description: Christian Turner bulldozes his way through multiple defenders for a Michigan TD to make it 31-0.
videos.headline: Turner drives his way through defenders for TD

videos.description: Shea Patterson continues to find pay dirt as he record his third touchdown of the game, this time as he dives into the pile.
videos.headline: Patterson notches 3rd touchdown with a push from his teammates

videos.description: Michigan backup QB Joe Milton runs the bootleg to pad Michigan's lead.
videos.headline: Michigan's backup QB gets in on the action with TD

videos.description: Michigan QB Joe Milton steps up in the pocket and fires a laser to a wide open Giles Jackson in the end zone for a 23-yard TD.
videos.headline: Milton finds Jackson wide open for 7th Michigan TD
